\s Mimi mgeni katika dunia
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mimi \bd*\bd m\bd*\bd geni katika dunia, ninasafiri kufika \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd . Hata ikiwa hatari njiani, nitaishinda pamoja na Mungu. Kama Ibrahimu majaribuni nita’vyoshinda kwa nguvu ya Mungu. Nitavumilia nifike \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd , ndilo kusudi la moyo. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Nikitembea gizani kabisa mimi mnyonge pamoja na \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , na nikipita\bd*\bd  Moto\bd*\bd ni, majini, nakusudia kufika \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd . Mungu ajua mapito jangwani, naye Mwenyezi atanifikisha. Nitavumilia nifike \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd , ndilo kusudi la moyo. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Tusisumbuke katika safari, tuwatazame wali’tangulia! \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  alitukomboa, \bd*\bd Msalaba\bd*\bd ni alitufilia! Naye atatufikisha \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd ; hivi tuimbe kwa mda kitambo: tutavumilia tufike \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd , ndilo kusudi la moyo! \bd*
